text: Ðis is þæra þreora hida landgemære æt nymed.
Ærest on copelan stan of ðæm stane west on herpoð on eisandune þonne þanon west on herpoð on readan flodan þonon on Secgbroces heafod þonne on adune on secgbroc oð Seo lacu scyt west.

Þanon ut on hæðfeld on seohteres heafod of þam seohtere adune on hane ðanon adune &lang streames oð riscbroc scyt on nymed þanon east on riscbroc on scipbroc þonne up on scipbroc ðæt eft on copelan stan.
Ðis is ðara ðreora hida boc æt Nymed ðe Eadgar cing gebocude Ælfhere his ðegne on ece yrfe.
